[h4 
	" The T'soa Airport
	$LF
	[a id=heading-5094 
	]a
]h4
[p 
	"With a well timed jump, you can skip the puzzle that forces you to deactivate three lasers. 
	$LF
	"With Sword Climb active you aren't moved by the fans
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"The first boss fight, very straight forward, you can just simply wait above the chute for the mice and hold b to grab them as soon as you can. The blades don't do enough damage to kill you.
	$LF
]p
