[h4 
	" The Water Kingdom
	$LF
	[a id=heading-5095 
	]a
]h4
[p 
	"You can pull the lever  to raise the pillars from under the platform.
	$LF
	"At the pillar you slice down, you can walk across it while it falls, the animation isn't the actual collision
	$LF
